{"tid":553327,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★2017年4月「少年股神」料港樓價明年大跌 火燎森：今年盡沽收租物業","createTime":"2018-02-07T10:44:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-07T07:07:22.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"addc022dee28a24c9b5ee997973b51737a26af7f","tid":553327,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T10:44:33.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】曾獲外界形容為「少年股神」的火燎森（化名），2003年跟隨股神巴菲特買入中國石油（0857）後，4年間一直抵押股票借錢再買，至2007年再跟股神出貨，加上其他股票亦有斬獲，賺近2000萬元。炒股勁賺後他轉買磚頭，在2007及2008年購入3個將軍澳住宅單位收租至今；近年他更進軍日本房地產及泰國基建項目。投資有道的他接受訪問時認為，目前本港樓市根本無投資價值，料隨着<span style=\"color: red;\">明年美國及中國政經環境惡化，樓價隨時大跌</span>，他計劃在今年餘下時間分批沽出手上香港物業。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/columnist2.php?col=1463481152363&amp;node=1491420154080&amp;issue=20170406\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Fcolumnist2.php%3Fcol%3D1463481152363%26node%3D1491420154080%26issue%3D20170406&d=0NtIp6AWbsTciRjD%2FUosWGowyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=d2e04826\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/columnist2.php?col=1463481152363&amp;node=1491420154080&amp;issue=20170406</a>"},{"pid":"5e0da7eb0277f3a4aeed53b006dedbb04aad4201","tid":553327,"uid":4917,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T10:46:36.000Z","msg":"專家食屎啦"},{"pid":"0d6408495e28a85dbc4f343bd6e47a785f0ed9a7","tid":553327,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T10:47:31.000Z","msg":"明年美國及中國政經環境惡化，樓價隨時大跌<br />\n明年美國及中國政經環境惡化，樓價隨時大跌<br />\n明年美國及中國政經環境惡化，樓價隨時大跌<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"243ad99dacbb23111a4fc5ef3362671aeefd55e8","tid":553327,"uid":90,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T11:37:22.000Z","msg":"之前教人買bitcoin個個？"},{"pid":"8641a7198e76893404787c843a24df64ef844cdd","tid":553327,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"243ad99dacbb23111a4fc5ef3362671aeefd55e8","tid":553327